By using our service, you agree that we may collect and use information about you in line with this privacy statement. Our primary goal in collecting Personal Information is to offer and improve the Service. Unless otherwise specified in this Privacy Statement, we will not use or disclose your information for any purpose other than that mentioned in this Privacy Statement.
