Information Gathering and Making Use of It:
During your use of our Service, we may ask you to provide us with some personally-identifying information to enhance your overall experience. We will retain and use the information you give in line with the terms of this confidentiality statement.
 Log Data:
We wish to notify you that whenever you use our Service, in the event of an app mistake, we collect data and information on your phone called Log Data (through third-party products). This Log Data may comprise your device’s Internet Protocol (“IP”) address, device name, operating system version, the app configuration used to access our Service, and other data.
Cookies:
Cookies are little data files that are frequently utilized as anonymous unique identifiers. These are sent to your browser by the websites you visit and are kept in the internal memory of your device.
It is not clear whether or not the service makes use of these "cookies." Although the app may make use of third-party code and libraries, such as "cookies," it may also make use of third-party code and libraries that collect information and improve their services. Accepting or declining these cookies is entirely up to you, and you can choose whether or not to be notified when a cookie is sent to your device. In the event that you reject our cookies, you may be unable to access or use certain features of this Service.
Providers of Services:
We may employ the services of third-party organizations and individuals for a variety of reasons, including but not limited to:
To supply our services on our behalf, to make it available; to perform service-related duties; or to assist us in evaluating how our Service is being utilized.
The fact that these third parties may have access to Personal Information about users of this Service is something we would want to bring to their attention. Their performance on our behalf will be monitored in order to guarantee they fulfill the obligations that have been assigned to them by us. They are, however, barred from releasing or otherwise exploiting the information for any other purpose than those specified.
Security:
We appreciate that you have placed your trust in us by entrusting us with your Personal Information, and as a result, we are committed to protecting it with commercially reasonable precautions. Keep in mind, however, that no type of internet transmission or electronic storage is totally secure or dependable, and we cannot ensure the complete security of any data transmitted or stored via the internet.
Other Platforms:
